    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223740/extras/5909d351d97cdabae503fc9a3fe635de.poster.avif?t=1753898806\" width=600 height=358 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223740/extras/5909d351d97cdabae503fc9a3fe635de.webm?t=1753898806\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223740/extras/5909d351d97cdabae503fc9a3fe635de.mp4?t=1753898806\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Fire in the Dark 是一款多人等距竞技场射击游戏，您可以邀请朋友与您一起对战。在中世纪的奇幻小城中，您将化身为两个女巫，在夜晚的决斗中相互对决。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223740/extras/56e921663d38c9ed66bc6e99e19f24df.poster.avif?t=1753898806\" width=450 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223740/extras/56e921663d38c9ed66bc6e99e19f24df.webm?t=1753898806\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223740/extras/56e921663d38c9ed66bc6e99e19f24df.mp4?t=1753898806\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>玩转阴影，躲在灌木丛中，追赶对手，打败他，证明谁才是最强的！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223740/extras/e8fd6cac8433fd23586e0c420d5f76f8.poster.avif?t=1753898806\" width=600 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223740/extras/e8fd6cac8433fd23586e0c420d5f76f8.webm?t=1753898806\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223740/extras/e8fd6cac8433fd23586e0c420d5f76f8.mp4?t=1753898806\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>使用火球造成伤害，点燃火把或烧毁灌木丛！<br>或者，依靠冰箭减慢敌人的速度并熄灭光源，以便谨慎地隐藏起来，等待合适的时机发动攻击！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223740/extras/1466b7e450255cb5535085fd8a2eeb21.poster.avif?t=1753898806\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223740/extras/1466b7e450255cb5535085fd8a2eeb21.webm?t=1753898806\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223740/extras/1466b7e450255cb5535085fd8a2eeb21.mp4?t=1753898806\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
